mobile_assistant_for_pregnant_women.description:
The system allows pregnant women to easily get all the necessary information at a particular stage of pregnancy about what they need to eat and drink, how to exercise, what their baby looks like (if its a smart phone app), how much they are supposed to weight, what symptoms they might have and the ways to feels better etc. All they need to do is to send and SMS (or send data via smart phone app) saying how long they have been pregnant. The system then automatically sends all the necessary data at particular time (Ex.: once a week). (See picture for more details)&#13;
&#13;
