mhealth_financing.description:
Through mobile money, governments and organizations can improve efficiencies in the transfer of funds and introduce better checks and balances. Individuals can benefit from a secure and reliable means to pay (and save) for health care costs. &#13;
&#13;
These efficiencies could be reached through 4 different examples:&#13;
1. Paying salaries of health care workers&#13;
2. Paying incentives to health care providers based on performance &#13;
3. Reimbursing health care providers for services delivered &#13;
4. Using voucher-based systems for micro health

